---
title: HelloHero: Chermoula-Spiced Roast Lamb with Garlic Veggie Crush, Pear Slaw & Balsamic Glaze
description: You might need a pair of sunglasses for this meal because it’s blinding, especially with garlic, potato and carrot combined into a sunset veggie crush. What goes better with veggies than a lamb roast of course, and this one is succulent, tender and drizzled in a balsamic sauce for a dark tone. Trust us, it tastes just as good as it looks.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
